graph LR
    TrustyAI[TrustyAI Service Operator]

    %% External Dependencies
    TrustyAI -->|platform runtime| K8s[Kubernetes/OpenShift<br/>1.19+/4.6+<br/>Required]
    TrustyAI -->|metrics scraping| PrometheusOp[Prometheus Operator<br/>Optional]
    TrustyAI -->|user authentication| OpenShiftOAuth[OpenShift OAuth<br/>OpenShift only]
    TrustyAI -->|traffic routing| Istio[Istio Service Mesh<br/>KServe serverless mode]
    TrustyAI -->|TLS certificates| CertManager[cert-manager<br/>1.13+<br/>Alternative to service-ca]
    TrustyAI -->|workload queuing| Kueue[Kueue<br/>v0.6+<br/>LM eval jobs]
    TrustyAI -->|data storage| Database[PostgreSQL/MySQL<br/>Alternative to PVC]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    TrustyAI -->|model serving<br/>CRD Watch/Patch| KServe[KServe]
    TrustyAI -->|payload processors<br/>Pod Exec/ConfigMap| ModelMesh[Model Mesh]
    TrustyAI -->|shared storage<br/>PVC| DSP[Data Science Pipelines]
    TrustyAI -.->|user interface<br/>CRD Creation| Dashboard[ODH Dashboard]

    %% Integration Points
    Dashboard -->|creates services| TrustyAI
    Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines] -.->|monitoring integration| TrustyAI

    %% External Services
    TrustyAI -->|model storage| S3[S3-compatible Storage]
    TrustyAI -->|models/datasets| HuggingFace[Hugging Face Hub]
    TrustyAI -->|API operations| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server]

